\id 3JN - Dawro
\h 3 Yohaannisa
\toc2 3 Yohaannisa
\toc1 3 Yohaannisa
\mt1 Yohaannisi
\mt2 Xaafeedda Heezzentho Kiitaa
\imt1 Geluwaa
\ip Yohaannisa heezzentho kiitaa, Yesuusi kiitteedda ammaniyaa asaa kaalethiyaa cimaa Yohaannisi xaafeedda. I xaafeeddawekka Gaayoosa giya itti woosa golliyaa kaalethiyaawaassa. Xaafii, Gaayoosi hara ammaniyaawantta maaddeedda diraw A galatee; hara bagganna qassi Diyootiraafisa geetettiyaa metuwaa medhdhiyaa bitaniyaappe naagettana mala akeekissee.
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatuwaassi Imetteedda Qantha Qofatuwaa
\io1 Geluwaa (1-4)
\io1 Gaayoosi galatettowaa (5-8)
\io1 Diyootiraafise naagettanaadan odettowaa (9-10)
\io1 Dimexiroosi galatettowaa (11-12)
\io1 Wurssethaa qutiyaa (13-15)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Taani ammaniyaawantta kaalethiyaa cimay, tumu siiqiyaa ta siiquwaa Gaayoosaw ha dabidaabbiyaa xaafay. \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Kit 19:29; Rom 16:23; 1Qo 1:14\x*
\v 2 Ta siiqoo, neeni Xoossaanna de7iyaa de7uu lo77a gidiyaawaa taani eriyaawaadan, neena ayayiinne waayissenna malanne qassi ne asatethay paxa gidana mala, Xoossaa woossay.
\v 3 Ayissi gooppe, amareedda ishatuu yiide, ubba wode neeni tumatethaan de7iyaawaanne ne tumatethaabaa markkatteedda wode, taani daro nashettaaddi.
\v 4 Ta naanay \f + \fr 1:4 \fq Ta naanay: \ft Godaa ammaniide kaalliyaawantta guussaa.\f* tumatethaan de7iyaawaa sisiyaawaappe aadhdhiide, taana nashechchiyaabay baawa.
\s1 Gaayoosabaa Asay Markkattee
\p 
\v 5 Ta siiqoo, nu ishatuu imatha gidooppekka, neeni unttunttoo oothiyaa oosuwaa ubbaan ammanetteedda oosuwaa oothaadda.
\v 6 Qassi unttunttu ne siiquwaabaa ammaniyaa asatoo markkatteeddino; unttunttu qanxxennaan bare ogiyaa baana mala Xoossay dosiyaawaadan, neeni lo77obaa oothaade unttuntta maaddaarikkii.
\v 7 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa ammanennawnttuppe ayinne akkennaan, Kiristtoosa sunthaa diraw keseeddino.
\v 8 Hewaa diraw, nuuni tumatethaa unttunttunna ittippe oothana mala, hawanttu mala asatuwaa maaddanaw bessee.
\s1 Diyootiraafise Seeretteedda; Dimexiroosi Sabetteedda
\p 
\v 9 Taani ammaniyaawanttoo, dabidaabbiyaa xaafaaddi; shin unttunttu kaappuwaa gidanaw koyyiyaa Diyootiraafise nuuni giyaawaa akkenna.
\v 10 Hewaa diraw, taani yaa biya wode, I nu bollan haasayiyaa iita haasayaanne I ootheedda oosuwaa hinttenttoo odana; qassi I hewe guuxxeedda giide, nu ishatuu yiyaa wode mokkenna; haray atto unttuntta mokkanaw koyyiyaawanttakka diggiide, ammaniyaawanttu giddoppe kessee.
\p 
\v 11 Ta siiqoo, lo77obaappe attin, iitabaa malatoppa. Lo77obaa oothiyaa ooninne Xoossaa asaa; shin iitabaa oothiyaa ooninne Xoossaa erenna.
\p 
\v 12 Dimexiroosi lo77a gidiyaawaa asay ubbay markkattee; tumatethay bare huuphiyankka aabaa markkattee. Nuunikka qassi aabaa markkatteetto; nu markkatethay tuma gidiyaawaa hinttekka eriita.
\s1 Wurssethaa Sarotaa
\p 
\v 13 Taani new xaafanaw koyyeedda darobay de7ee; shin waraqataaninne qalamiyaaninne xaafanaw koyyikke.
\v 14 Shin taani matan neenanna gakkettanaw qoppay; he wode nuuni gakeettiide haasayana.
\p 
\v 15 Sarotethay neenanna gido.
\p Ne dabbatuu neena saro saro yaagiino. Nu dabbatuwaa ubbaa unttunttu sunthaa sunthaa xeesaade, taana saro saro geedda yaaga.
